description: An ancient estuary cataloged by Ptolemy. BAtlas was only confident enough to locate it somewhere in modern Somerset, listing it as an "unlocated" feature in the Map-by-Map Directory. Other scholarly suggestions include the Axe and the Parrett rivers.
